# ==================================================
# Keep These (Important!)
# ==================================================
# DO NOT IGNORE:
# - .env.example (safe template)
# - render.yaml (deployment config - but check for secrets!)
# - Procfile (deployment config)
# - All source code files
# - Documentation (*.md)

